ğŸ§  THEORY NOTES (Simple)
What is Machine Learning (ML)?

Machine Learning means:

â€œInstead of writing rules manually, we train a model from data.â€

Funny example:

If you try to write spam rules manually, youâ€™ll end up like:

â€œIf message contains â€˜FREEâ€™, mark spamâ€

â€œIf message contains â€˜WINâ€™, mark spamâ€

â€œIf message contains â€˜CONGRATULATIONSâ€™, mark spamâ€

But spammers will write:

â€œFrâ‚¬â‚¬â€

â€œW1nâ€

â€œCongratzzzzâ€

So ML is like hiring a smart bouncer who learns spam behavior from examples.

